trans-unit.source: Defines the methods called during contract generation that can be used to modify the generated code for a service contract.
trans-unit.target: 定义可用来修改服务协定生成的代码的协定生成期间调用的方法。

trans-unit.source: Implement the IServiceContractGenerationExtension interface on a contract behavior (a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior?displayProperty=fullName> type) to enable you to modify the code generated when a contract or endpoint is compiled into code.
trans-unit.target: 对协定行为实现 IServiceContractGenerationExtension 接口 (<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior?displayProperty=fullName>类型) 以使你能够修改协定或终结点编译为代码时生成的代码。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Typically, a custom <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> inserts a custom contract behavior into the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection during the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 通常情况下，自定义<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>插入<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName>到<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A>或<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A></xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A>在呼叫期间的集合</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName>自定义协定行为</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Implement to modify the code document object model prior to the contract generation process.
trans-unit.target: 实现此方法可以修改协定生成过程之前的代码文档对象模型。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerationContext?displayProperty=fullName> to modify the contract, operations, or the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerator?displayProperty=fullName> prior to code generation.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerationContext?displayProperty=fullName>修改协定、 操作或<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerator?displayProperty=fullName>在代码生成之前。</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerator?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerationContext?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The code generated context to use to modify the code document prior to generation.
trans-unit.target: 上下文用于修改代码文档生成之前生成的代码。
